    "body": "Just for future reference, so it doesn't get lost in the IRC logs:\n[17:52] <+Phrohdoh> https://github.com/Phrohdoh/OpenRA/commit/8cee27b71cd077d5ab89e0d2f7a2ed4283ada62b if anyone wants it\n\nI haven't tested it, but it seems like it should fix the crash.\nMy only comment on that is that setting `isTransitioning = false;` should most likely be done inside the `after` action of `PlayCustomAnimation()` and `PlayCustomAnimationBackwards()`.\n"
